{110}{}{我们被雇佣兵组织、赏金猎人追捕，你能想到的……但我们设法保持低调。出乎意料的是，当我遇到一个了解我的人后，我对荒地监狱的怀疑得到了证实……我被指控谋杀并被带走之前的生活。。。 -- We were chased by mercenary groups, bounty hunters, you name it... But we managed to keep a low profile. Unexpectedly, my suspicions about the wasteland prison were confirmed after I met the person who knew all about me... My life before I was accused of murder and taken away...}
