### {112}{}{Maybe, I don't know... I just couldn't live like that, everything seemed strange, people looking at me... So I decided to leave all that behind and continue my work, to unravel the truth behind the curtain. But one thing stands in front of others...}
{112}{}{也许，我不知道。。。我就是不能那样生活，一切似乎都很奇怪，人们看着我……所以我决定把这一切抛在脑后，继续我的工作，揭开幕后的真相。但有一件事摆在其他人面前。。。 -- Maybe, I don't know... I just couldn't live like that, everything seemed strange, people looking at me... So I decided to leave all that behind and continue my work, to unravel the truth behind the curtain. But one thing stands in front of others...}
