### {116}{}{Well, you're right. Something is missing in there. I can recognize a bonehead when I see one!}
{116}{}{你说得对。里面少了什么东西。当我看到一个骨头时，我能认出它！ -- Well, you're right. Something is missing in there. I can recognize a bonehead when I see one!}
### {117}{}{Believe me, you'll get used to it. The truth is painful but the sooner we accept it, the sooner we can go on with our lives. You know... this situation... we could both benefit from it. With my help, you can find out what happened to you if that's what you want.}
{117}{}{相信我，你会习惯的。真相是痛苦的，但我们越早接受它，我们就能越早继续我们的生活。你知道。。。这种情况。。。我们都可以从中受益。在我的帮助下，如果你想要的话，你可以知道你发生了什么。 -- Believe me, you'll get used to it. The truth is painful but the sooner we accept it, the sooner we can go on with our lives. You know... this situation... we could both benefit from it. With my help, you can find out what happened to you if that's what you want.}
### {118}{}{Yeah, I guess... What do you get from all this?}
{118}{}{是的，我想。。。你从这一切中得到了什么？ -- Yeah, I guess... What do you get from all this?}
