{121}{}{哦，别逗我笑。。。[和他的男人说话。]你确定这是对的人吗。。。？我不这么认为。这是一个愚蠢的混蛋。。。杀了这个婊子养的！ -- Oh, don't make me laugh... [Talking to his man.] Are you sure this is the right guy...? I don't think so. This is one stupid motherfucker... Kill the son of a bitch!}
