{134}{}{如果我们整件事都错了怎么办？ -- What if we are wrong about the whole thing?}
### {135}{}{Because YOU are not the one they are looking for. But most of all you were there, you've seen things, don't tell me you feel nothing about what they have done to you... what they have taken from you. Going back might be hard I know, but think about what you will earn from this... Answers about who you really are.}
{135}{}{因为你不是他们要找的那个人。但最重要的是，你在那里，你看到了一些事情，不要告诉我你对他们对你所做的一切毫无感觉。。。他们从你身上夺走了什么。我知道回去可能很难，但想想你会从中赚什么。。。关于你真实身份的答案。 -- Because YOU are not the one they are looking for. But most of all you were there, you've seen things, don't tell me you feel nothing about what they have done to you... what they have taken from you. Going back might be hard I know, but think about what you will earn from this... Answers about who you really are.}
