{136}{}{这就是我这么做的唯一原因。我有什么有用的东西就回来。 -- Well, that's the only reason I'm doing this. I'll be back when I have something useful.}
### {137}{}{I know who I am... And my mission is to take you back where you belong whether you like it or not!}
