### {138}{}{Then we wouldn't be here having this conversation. Look, if you don't understand it's in our best interest to help each other then our talk is done. Furthermore, I think you are trying to slow us down! Let me tell you something... [Turns to his men.] Get rid of this scumbag, he's useless!}
{138}{}{那我们就不会在这里进行这种对话了。听着，如果你不明白互相帮助最符合我们的利益，那么我们的谈话就结束了。此外，我认为你是想让我们慢下来！让我告诉你一件事。。。[转向他的手下。]除掉这个卑鄙小人，他没用！ -- Then we wouldn't be here having this conversation. Look, if you don't understand it's in our best interest to help each other then our talk is done. Furthermore, I think you are trying to slow us down! Let me tell you something... [Turns to his men.] Get rid of this scumbag, he's useless!}
